import { Link } from "react-router-dom";
import {
  Box,
  TextField,
  MenuItem,
  FormControl,
  Typography,
  Grid,
  Divider,
  Chip,
} from "@mui/material";
import { LoadingButton } from "@mui/lab";

const LoginPage = () => {
  return (
    <Box
      component="div"
      sx={{
        display: "flex",
        flexDirection: "column",
        flexWrap: "wrap",
        maxWidth: 400,
        border: ".1px solid lightgray",
        boxShadow: "0.5px 0.5px 5px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, .1)",
        borderRadius: ".3rem",
      }}
      mt={12}
      ml="auto"
      mr="auto"
      p={4}
      gap={2}
    >
      <Typography variant="h4" fontWeight="bold">
        Conectare
      </Typography>
      <Box component="form">
        <Grid
          container
          spacing={2}
          sx={{ alignItems: "center", justifyContent: "center" }}
        >
          <Grid item xs={12}>
            <FormControl fullWidth>
              <TextField
                type="email"
                label="Email"
                variant="outlined"
                size="small"
                required
              />
            </FormControl>
          </Grid>
          <Grid item xs={12}>
            <FormControl fullWidth>
              <TextField
                type="password"
                label="Parolă"
                variant="outlined"
                size="small"
                required
              />
            </FormControl>
          </Grid>
        </Grid>
      </Box>
      <LoadingButton
        variant="contained"
        loadingPosition="center"
        sx={{
          fontSize: "1rem",
          alignSelf: "flex-start",
          textTransform: "capitalize",
          backgroundColor: "primary.main",
          "&:hover": { backgroundColor: "primary.dark" },
        }}
      >
        Conectare
      </LoadingButton>
      <Typography variant="body1" component="span">
        Nu ai un cont? Înregistrează-te de{" "}
        <Link to="/register">
          <Typography
            sx={{ color: "primary.main" }}
            variant="body1"
            component="span"
          >
            aici!
          </Typography>
        </Link>
      </Typography>
    </Box>
  );
};

export default LoginPage;
